      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">19.502-1</ph> Requirements for setting
aside acquisitions.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1159e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1180e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> The contracting officer shall
set aside an individual acquisition or class of acquisitions for
competition among small businesses when-</p>
               <ol id="d1159e23" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1180e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> It is determined
to be in the interest of maintaining or mobilizing the <ph rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?>Nation’s<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 19.502-1 by—
a.Removing from paragraph (a)(1) “Nations” and adding “Nation’s” in its place;?></ph> full productive
capacity, war or national defense programs; or</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d1180e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> Assuring
that a fair proportion of Government contracts in each industry <ph rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?>is<?FM MARKER [Why] b. Removing from paragraph (a)(2) “category”; and?></ph> placed with small
business concerns; and the circumstances described in <xref href="FAR-i1100762.dita#i1100762"
                              base="i1100762"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.502-2</xref> or <xref href="FAR-i1100796.dita#i1100796"
                              base="i1100796"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">19.502-3</xref>(a) exist.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d1180e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> 
                  <ph rev="FAC 2020-05 March 30, 2020" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2014-002?>This requirement does not
apply to purchases of $3,500 or less ($20,000 or less for acquisitions
as described in <xref href="FAR-i1111870.dita#i1111870"
                           base="i1111870"
                           outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                           class="- topic/xref ">13.201</xref>(g)(1)),
or purchases from required sources under <xref href="FAR-i1118293.dita#i1118293"
                           base="i1118293"
                           outputclass="fm:Part"
                           class="- topic/xref ">part  8 </xref>(e.g., Committee
for Purchase From People Who are Blind or Severely Disabled).<?FM MARKER [Why] c. Revising paragraph (b).?></ph>
               </p>
            </li>
         </ol>
